	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />How to change or edit mapper for NES.? Coz some game have strange mapper and can't run on emulator so I want to know how to modify or fix it to normal mapper.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

