	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />There are two solutions, and both of them require programming.
<br /><ol style="list-style-type: lower-alpha"><li>Mapper hacking: Find a mapper similar in capability, change every mapper access to use the other mapper, and share the IPS. </li><li>Download a Free emulator, write a driver for this mapper, and share the source code patch. </li></ol>

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


